---------------------------------------------------------------------------

EUROPE: Professors to select new scientific council

Cayley Dobie
Six European professors have been appointed to the European Research
Council=92s identification committee charged with finding new members for i=
ts
scientific council.
Full report on the University World News site:
http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?story=3D20100925155749601

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

DENMARK: Interest in Brazilian studies up

Jan Petter Myklebust
A Danish university department spec ialising in Brazilian studies has
doubled its student numbers since 2009.
Full report on the University World News site:
http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?story=3D20100925155704308
