an></td></tr></table></font><br><font color=3D"#003366"><span style=3D"colo=
r: #003366">This week=92s edition of University World News publishes a spec=
ial report on exporting online education, edited by <B><I>PHILIP FINE</I></=
B>, and <B><I>JOHN WALSHE</I></B> reports from a European Universities Asso=
